    "description": "让自己沉浸在神秘公寓的黑暗中，每个阴影都隐藏着可怕的秘密。踏上惊心动魄的探索之旅，发现每一步都尾随着你的邪恶存在背后的真相。<br><br>在这款身临其境的恐怖游戏中，你扮演乔尔，他在一个陌生的公寓里醒来，失去了记忆。当你探索黑暗而破旧的房间时，令人不安的线索揭示了一场涉及神秘失踪儿童的古老犯罪的痕迹。但要小心，你并不孤单......<br><br>运用你的聪明才智和勇气来逃离这种无处不在的威胁，并解开困扰这些地方的谜团。现实和噩梦之间的界限是模糊的，你所做的每一个决定都可以让你更接近真相或你的结局。<br><br>你敢于发现黑暗中隐藏着什么吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045770/extras/7f2cfd88b1ec8caeaddafc9bd987d1fc.poster.avif?t=1723766447\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045770/extras/7f2cfd88b1ec8caeaddafc9bd987d1fc.webm?t=1723766447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>压抑的气氛、身临其境的图形和配乐将让你沉浸在恐怖的气氛中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045770/extras/b6e38b7456c6270e757ad5bba6f46dbf.poster.avif?t=1723766447\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045770/extras/b6e38b7456c6270e757ad5bba6f46dbf.webm?t=1723766447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><u>游戏时长：45-60分钟</u>",
